  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This monocentric registry should provide information on the extent how patients with
      pulmonary diseases such as pulmonary hypertension will benefit from rehabilitation treatment.
      The data may provide a basis for further prospective studies showing the treatment of
      patients with pulmonary diseases especially by physical activation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
